{"tid":811752,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"細個拎乜嘢餸飯","createTime":"2018-09-09T05:50:21.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-10T09:13:48.000Z","uid":67144,"like":6,"dislike":20,"uniUserReply":50,"replies":[{"pid":"3a45111b3339bd3825cb606ecfb795c8004eae47","tid":811752,"uid":67144,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-09T05:50:21.000Z","msg":"細個我極討厭食飯<br />\n然後我姑姐就諗到如果我食一啖飯<br />\n就可以即刻食一塊熱浪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一係就熱浪加飯一齊食<br />\n細個覺得好正<br />\n但依加諗翻起<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我諗起係因為我見到表妹<br />\n依加3歲拎熊仔糖餸飯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4578d4350fff34f96271f3e444e03720b66988c9","tid":811752,"uid":6636,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-09T05:51:41.000Z","msg":"咸強<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59a6bc3a03d5c6f2a4ff6fa8be36aef1a4c84a3b","tid":811752,"uid":146435,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-09T05:55:12.000Z","msg":"電視"},{"pid":"5b18063bc53c24824c6df4ffea5d161dfc6d0131","tid":811752,"uid":82450,"like":1,"dislike":11,"score":-10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-09T05:55:26.000Z","msg":"香蕉 <br />\n香蕉加飯 真係好撚好食"},{"pid":"81b73a4c904af7d1a278c7a698cfbad44d4c5571","tid":811752,"uid":89449,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-09T05:56:40.000Z","msg":"豉油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"810cc268478a9520b76e1c23e7792c7b70797604","tid":811752,"uid":203474,"like":4,"dislike":4,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-09T05:57:25.000Z","msg":"美極<br />\n<br />\n撈飯一流<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.g