/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n白飯本身就得澱粉質 唔存在營唔營養<br />\n另外 如果撈落去嘅野唔健康 咁分開食都一樣唔健康<br />\n<br />\n韓國啲湯飯又唔健康？<br />\n日本啲茶漬飯又唔健康？<br />\n<br />\n聽咗撈飯唔健康咁多年，根本就係同燙傷要搽豉油一撚樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"18db0b0ce3fb9dd082acac169c47c1954b3f5451","tid":811752,"uid":1750,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-10T03:35:24.000Z","msg":"茄汁焗豆"},{"pid":"23327c5f312bd528b04ec0926b718e720d229c30","tid":811752,"uid":165368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-10T03:47:40.000Z","msg":"蒸翼"},{"pid":"fab1dee137c8829dd537381f3b85cbeb61478a14","tid":811752,"uid":79145,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-10T05:08:17.000Z","msg":"蒜蓉辣椒醬"},{"pid":"001c6ff344a4c3c9e0c4076af39791482e4f4f3f","tid":811752,"uid":136985,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-10T05:11:06.000Z","msg":"雞粉"},{"pid":"58d4c9f16b1705ce14377f179da99350037ef861","tid":811752,"uid":52369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-10T05:20:50.000Z","msg":"魚翅"},{"pid":"207c19196e10647f34455dfbc45d71788e0b6d12","tid":811752,"uid":162401,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-10T05:22:46.000Z","msg":"豉油麻油"},{"pid":"e8ab0f36d8953a96c16d0d4610e41b522f7f0606","tid":811752,"uid":47647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-10T05:26:00.000Z","msg":"可樂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bdf1e5aa596bf35234eb983e2a6120352e7c8731","tid":811752,"uid":32464,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"eb530093b9f69d9aa55529c352b98fa330779047","tid":811752,"uid":136023,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"d24c7f3c8695ca967db5dad636cdbbfd798380a9","tid":811752,"uid":108756,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-09T07:27:43.000Z","msg":"點解呢度好似咁多人屋企會咁樣俾你地撈飯食 唔健康又對身體唔好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-10T01:18:32.000Z","msg":"關撈飯食咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n白飯本身就得澱粉質 唔存在營唔營養<br />\n另外 如果撈落去嘅野唔健康 咁分開食都一樣唔健康<br />\n<br />\n韓國啲湯飯又唔健康？<br />\n日本啲茶漬飯又唔健康？<br />\n<br />\n聽咗撈飯唔健康咁多年，根本就係同燙傷要搽豉油一撚樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-10T05:40:14.000Z","msg":"可能因為通常會分正餐同零食，而正餐通常食飯魚肉菜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以感覺上熱浪熊仔糖撈飯唔算正餐掛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}